PrecisAppointment of MARYANTONETT FLUMIAN, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure and as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission; effective July 3, 2001.
